<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: aiming accuracy -->
  <AimingAccuracy.label>瞄准精度</AimingAccuracy.label>
  <!-- EN: How well a shooter can lead moving targets and estimate range in combination with the weapon's aiming efficiency.\n\nThe final modifier is calculated via this formula:\n(1.5 - aiming accuracy) / aiming efficiency\n\nLead error is calculated by multiplying this factor against total lead distance in cells. Range error is calculated by multiplying it against the total distance to the target divided by 4.\n\nAiming accuracy influences the the sway reduction during aimed shots. For example, at 75% aiming accuracy sway will be reduced to 25%. -->
  <AimingAccuracy.description>射击者瞄准射击移动目标的能力，并结合武器的瞄准效率估算最终射程。\n\n最终判定数值根据以下公式计算：\n(1.5 - 瞄准精度) / 瞄准效率\n\n瞄准误差：瞄准距离格数*判定数值。\n射程误差：(总距离格数/4)*判定数值\n\n瞄准精度会影响瞄准射击过程中的武器晃动。例如，在瞄准精度为75%时，晃动幅度将减少至25%。</AimingAccuracy.description>
  
  <!-- EN: armor coverage -->
  <AverageSharpArmor.label>平均护甲值</AverageSharpArmor.label>
  <!-- EN: The average value of armor coverage across this person's body. Higher values will make them more confident against low-penetration projectiles. -->
  <AverageSharpArmor.description>这个人身上护甲平均值。数值越高，它们面对低穿透弹射物时更有信心。</AverageSharpArmor.description>
  <!-- EN: {0} mm RHA -->
  <AverageSharpArmor.formatString>{0} mm RHA</AverageSharpArmor.formatString>
  
  <!-- EN: body part MPa -->
  <BodyPartBluntArmor.label>身体防护能力(钝器)</BodyPartBluntArmor.label>
  <!-- EN: Compared against weapon's armor penetration to see if it can penetrate to the next layer of body parts. A high value means low-penetration attacks like buckshot will have a harder time hitting internal organs. -->
  <BodyPartBluntArmor.description>对比武器的装甲穿透力，看它是否能穿透到下一层身体部位。更高的数值意味着像霰弹这样的低穿透攻击将更难击中内脏。</BodyPartBluntArmor.description>
  <!-- EN: {0} MPa -->
  <BodyPartBluntArmor.formatString>{0} MPa</BodyPartBluntArmor.formatString>
  
  <!-- EN: body part RHA -->
  <BodyPartSharpArmor.label>身体防护能力(利器)</BodyPartSharpArmor.label>
  <!-- EN: Compared against weapon's armor penetration to see if it can penetrate to the next layer of body parts. A high value means low-penetration attacks like buckshot will have a harder time hitting internal organs. -->
  <BodyPartSharpArmor.description>对比武器的装甲穿透力，看它是否能穿透到下一层身体部位。更高的数值意味着像霰弹这样的低穿透攻击将更难击中内脏。</BodyPartSharpArmor.description>
